summary: Question to the people who were around the doctor who fandom 2005 when doctor who was renewed. I just watched the interview on...
body:
Question to the people who were around the doctor who fandom 2005 when doctor who was renewed. I just watched the interview on the season 1 DVD where Eccelston answers to the question if he will regenerate: “well compared to the lenght of the old seasons i allready filmed two seasons.” And he grins really big.

How did they kept that a scret back then? Where there no spoilers, nothing leaked? Was it a big surprise when he regenerated?
